{"tid":573861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「強國」GoBee Bike 大量單車被破壞，全面撤出X國市場。","createTime":"2018-02-27T00:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T06:09:23.000Z","uid":156363,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ca74e24c0c5c887dea0cc8edb63311cb78c005f1","tid":573861,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T00:56:34.000Z","msg":"本土共享單車企業宣佈完全撤出法國市場，並關閉該公司在法國所有城市的業務。據該公司表示，由於他們的單車受到大量破壞行為和濫用所困擾，所以決定退出法國市場，並向所有用戶退還帳號餘額及按金。<br />\n<br />\nGoBee Bike 在公告中表示，他們在歐洲成功吸引 15 萬名用戶，但由於大量破壞行為及濫用，令到旗下的單車慢慢變得無法使用。當中 3,200 部單車失靈，約 1,000 部單車被非法佔用，停泊在私人地方。而 GoBee Bike 一共需要派員處理當中 6,500 件個案。<br />\n<br />\n對初創企業而言，難以承受如此高昂的維護成本，而對用家來說，大量失靈的單車亦嚴重影響使用體驗。 GoBee Bike 已先後停止在比利時布魯塞爾，法國里爾及蘭斯的業務，早前亦退出了意大利市場。如今，巴黎及里昂的用戶亦無法再使用這項服務。而在 GoBee Bike 仍在發源地香港繼續提供服務。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，單在巴黎已經有 4 間不同的共享單車公司， Ofo 、 Mobike 、 Obike 及 GoBee Bike 。當中 Ofo 和 Mobike 都是實力雄厚的中國企業。據 CrunchBase 資料顯示， Ofo 及 Mobike 已籌集逾 20 億美元資金。相較之下， GoBee Bike僅籌得 900 萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n而 Ofo 及 Mobike 在進軍巴黎時，都以免費使用作推廣，成功搶得大量用戶。因此有評論認為， GoBee Bike 敗走法國的主因是資金不足。畢竟以初創企業來說，實在難以與免費服務競爭。"},{"pid":"001a527222a97eeb7ad7dee4c51ac80fb4d473a7","tid":573861,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T00:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/2-51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F2-51.jpg&h=3536f3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64502cf4fe97462012ec3fa10baca76de2310c52","tid":573861,"uid":45934,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T01:17:57.000Z","msg":"香港d車都好多比人夾爛左個鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人類就係咁殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cd277c829eb95197af50f1120ecbd68aec0c62","tid":573861,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64502cf4fe97462012ec3fa10baca76de2310c52","tid":573861,"uid":45934,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T01:17:57.000Z","msg":"香港d車都好多比人夾爛左個鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人類就係咁殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T01:29:15.000Z","msg":"反而財大氣粗既大陸公司就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1a0bf04c956b05a2bd06b4d3653e4ac3bebc45","tid":573861,"uid":109983,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:17:42.000Z","msg":"支那不意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5f9215045d4bfad82e48f4cf21519f5e7f77b9","tid":573861,"uid":5070,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:20:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24f9d48e23985900c9584b483101b3b07b7272a0","tid":573861,"uid":4525,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a5f9215045d4bfad82e48f4cf21519f5e7f77b9","tid":573861,"uid":5070,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"1e1a0bf04c956b05a2bd06b4d3653e4ac3bebc45","tid":573861,"uid":109983,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:17:42.000Z","msg":"支那不意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:20:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:23:50.000Z","msg":"競爭對手係邊個呀傻鳩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6207e15a474dfff97ee4e3045da0417888b03ff8","tid":573861,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24f9d48e23985900c9584b483101b3b07b7272a0","tid":573861,"uid":4525,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a5f9215045d4bfad82e48f4cf21519f5e7f77b9","tid":573861,"uid